Log:
  Fix the following bugs related to the SCTP support of netstat:
  * Correctly handle -a.
  * -A isn't supported.
  * Show all closed 1-to-1 and 1-to-many style sockets.
  * Show all listening 1-to-many style sockets.
  * Use consistent formatting for -W.

